fr.univnantes.atal.web.piubella.model

Enum CollectDay

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<CollectDay>
      • fr.univnantes.atal.web.piubella.model.CollectDay
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<CollectDay>

    public enum CollectDay
extends Enum<CollectDay>
    Enum to represent the different values possible of collect days. Indexes are used to deliver a small file as dataset. They must therefore be used to understand a call to the FetchJson servlet.
